from typing import Any, List, Optional, Union

from kittycad.api.api_tokens import list_api_tokens_for_user
from kittycad.client import ClientFromEnv
from kittycad.models import ApiTokenResultsPage, Error
from kittycad.models.created_at_sort_mode import CreatedAtSortMode
from kittycad.types import Response


def example_list_api_tokens_for_user():
    # Create our client.
    client = ClientFromEnv()

    result: Optional[
        Union[ApiTokenResultsPage, Error]
    ] = list_api_tokens_for_user.sync(
        client=client,
        sort_by=CreatedAtSortMode.CREATED_AT_ASCENDING,
        limit=None,  # Optional[int]
        page_token=None,  # Optional[str]
    )

    if isinstance(result, Error) or result == None:
        print(result)
        raise Exception("Error in response")

    body: ApiTokenResultsPage = result
    print(body)
